bellabeat-case-study

Hein Htet Naing (Hector)

2023-02-14

Objective (Ask):

To analyze smart device fitness trackers from the current market to discover the trend of consumer’s behavior to recommend suitable marketing strategy from the findings on one of the bellabeat products to the CEO.

Data source (Prepare):

The data is directly downloaded from Link. The data is a record logs of 30 Fitbit users’ activities from 03/12/2016 to 05/12/2016. A total of 18 CSV files split by each activity type, inside each CSV files, activity logs for each user has recorded in hourly or daily depending of the activities.

The data set is provided a Kaggle user Möbius who has a significant contribution to the Kaggle platform.

Credit: The usage of this data is only for capstone project without any business conduct, only for educational purposes.
